snippet.description:
The biggest, spiciest ad film of the year is HERE! 
Atlee x Ranveer Singh team up with Sreeleela & Bobby Deol for the wildest cinematic explosion of action, drama, comedy & masala.

Watch the explosive trailer of AGENT CHING ATTACKS with jaw-dropping action, whistle-worthy drama, foot-tapping music, and masala so hotтАж itтАЩll set your screen on fire.

The full film premieres Sunday, October 19 exclusively on this channel.

WHAT TO EXPECT:
тАв Ranveer Singh in his most powerful avatar yet as Agent Ching
тАв Sreeleela adding spice and swagger as Agent Mirchi
тАв Bobby Deol unleashing chaos as Professor White Noise
тАв Signature Atlee scale, style & spectacle with a global A-list crew
тАв A brand-new version of the iconic anthem тАЬMy Name is Ranveer ChingтАЭ

From Bhatinda to Beijing, thereтАЩs only one kingтАж Ranveer Ching!

This is the BIGGEST celebration of Desi Chinese ever тАФ bold, flavourful, cinematic, and guaranteed to #AagLagaDe.

About ChingтАЩs Secret - They say that to win Hindustani hearts even Chinese food became desi! And thereтАЩs only one Desi Chinese food brand that can make desi hearts beat faster тАУ ChingтАЩs. Saucy. Spicy. Sweet and sour. Hot and sour. Crunchy. Slurpy. Zesty. Schezwani. ManchurianтАж Whatever be the kind of Desi Chinese your palate craves for, only ChingтАЩs can hit the spot with a perfect zing.

I тЩе Desi Chinese!

snippet.title: Baahubali: The Epic (Official US Trailer 2)
snippet.description:
In theaters worldwide October 31, 2025!

Special First Day First Show screenings in IMAX and Premium Large Formats October 29, 2025!  

TICKETS ON SALE NOW

10 years before RRR took the world by storm, master filmmaker S.S. Rajamouli redefined Indian Cinema with his two-part BAAHUBALI saga. Now, the epic tale of royalty, revenge, kings, and wars has been personally re-edited by the master himself from two films into a single unforgettable cinematic experience, with fully remastered picture and sound (and a few new surprises), so audiences can reunite to experience the euphoria the way it was intended: on the big screen.

When a lost prince (Prabhas) is rescued and raised in exile, he grows up unaware of his past. Years later, he returns to uncover the truth about his fatherтАЩs murder and his motherтАЩs imprisonment, and must rise to reclaim his place as the rightful king.

The wait is over тАФ the Dhurandhar Title Track (Jogi) is finally here!
Packed with fierce beats, bold voices, and unstoppable energy тАФ this oneтАЩs pure fire. ЁЯФе

Releasing on 5th December 2025

Credits: 
Jio Studios Presents
A B62 Studios Production

An Aditya Dhar Film
DHURANDHAR

Written, Directed and Produced by: Aditya Dhar
Produced by: Jyoti Deshpande
Produced by: Lokesh Dhar

Cast: Ranveer Singh | Sanjay Dutt | Akshaye Khanna | R. Madhavan | Arjun Rampal | Sara Arjun

Audio Credits:
Original Song Name: Na De Dil Pardesi Nu (Jogi)

Music: Shashwat Sachdev, Charanjit Ahuja
Produced and Arranged: Shashwat Sachdev
Singers: Hanumankind, Jasmine Sandlas, Sudhir Yaduvanshi, Shashwat Sachdev, Mohd. Sadiq, Ranjit Kaur

Music Video: Jayesh Shikarkhane & Team

Assistant engineers: Jazbaat, Sohamm, Suryansh
HanumanKind vocals mixed by Akash Shravan

You are not ready for this

Je jar mera mainu zehar zehar zehar

Get ready!

Father, Forgive me, I can't forgive them. You know my history, you know what I did then. What I do now, a whole lot worse. Heavy is the head, it's a blessing and a curse.

snippet.title: Nafrat Official Music Video | Darshan Raval | Sandipa D | Akshay K | Naushad Khan | Indie Music
snippet.description:
An emotionally charged composition by Darshan Raval that delves deep into the turmoil of anger, betrayal, and heartbreak. It expresses the raw pain of trusting someone who ends up breaking that very trust, leaving behind scars that never fade. Sung and composed by Darshan Raval, with heartfelt lyrics by Noor, the song beautifully blends emotion and melody to portray the darker side of love. Featuring Sandeepa Dhar, the music video powerfully captures the intensity of disappointment and the inevitable journey from love to Nafrat.

Lyrics : Noor

Pardesiya..
Hai tere pyar mein jab se
Jhankaar si..
Hai dil ke taar mein tab se

Tum ho mere jaanta hun magar
Pohchaau├▒ tum tak ye kaise khabar

Kab se hun main ummeed mei├▒
Hai ankaha jo sun lo agar

Pardesiya..
Mila hai tu mujhe jab se

Mai├▒ qaid hu├▒
Tere bhi pyar mein tab se ..

Pardesiya hai├▒ teri batiyo├▒ ne 
Kiya pareshan pardesiya..

Pardesiya hai├▒ teri ankhiyo├▒ ke
Dil pe nishaan pardesiya..
 
Chhoo ke labo├▒ se jaise
Jaadu hi kar diya
Saavan ne morni ko
Qaabu mein kar liya

Hum dono ki juda thee├▒ hastiyaa├▒
Ho├▒ kinara bin jaise kashtiyaa├▒

Aasaan ho aage safar
Tum saath mera chun lo agar

Pardesiya.. 

#SonuNigam #SidharthMalhotra #JanhviKapoor
